data.description: Just a beautiful country setting here on 1 acre! Home has 3 bedrooms with possibly a 4th or you could use as office and more. Also here you have just a great 24 x 30  shop finished walls and ceiling with electric , concrete floor, and garage door with automatic garage opener. Spacious living room with nice window views. New paint and some new flooring and fixtures plus more! Great front deck to sit on enjoy that morning coffee and watch the wildlife! Republic schools . You get it all here country setting but easy drive to town. You need to see this one! Buyers to do own due diligence on property sq footage and property lines.
